'From Squeak3.1alpha [latest update: #''Squeak3.1alpha'' of 5 February 2001 update 3932] on 19 April 2001 at 11:26:26 am'!"Change Set:		psPrintFixDate:			19 April 2001Author:			Bob Arningfix postscript printing of ProjectViewMorph (the name inside was not printing)"!!ProjectViewMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'RAA 4/19/2001 11:25'!fullDrawPostscriptOn: aCanvas	| f |	"handle the fact that we have the squished text within"	f _ self imageForm.	f offset: 0@0.	aCanvas paintImage: f at: bounds origin.! !